00:00:02.135 --> 00:00:03.771 position:19% line:83% align:start
[narrator] Do you seek
adventure beyond

00:00:03.872 --> 00:00:05.472 position:13% line:89% align:start
the treacherous waterfalls?

00:00:05.573 --> 00:00:07.509 position:7% line:89% align:start
Do you seek the mythical being

00:00:07.609 --> 00:00:10.344 position:24% line:83% align:start
that dwells in this
unreachable place?

00:00:10.444 --> 00:00:14.682 position:24% line:83% align:start
If you do, then you
must first find me.

00:00:14.782 --> 00:00:17.317 position:16% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music playing]

00:00:19.353 --> 00:00:22.055 position:24% line:89% align:start
[thunder crashing]

00:00:26.561 --> 00:00:28.028 position:35% line:89% align:start
[rumbling]

00:00:31.331 --> 00:00:34.368 position:10% line:89% align:start
[narrator] The year is 1889.

00:00:34.468 --> 00:00:36.403 position:30% line:83% align:start
Countless ships
are being consumed

00:00:36.504 --> 00:00:38.806 position:27% line:83% align:start
beneath the waves
of the Atlantic Ocean.

00:00:38.907 --> 00:00:42.544 position:13% line:83% align:start
The people whisper in fear
about terrible sea monsters.

00:00:42.644 --> 00:00:45.178 position:21% line:83% align:start
However, governments
of the world suspect

00:00:45.279 --> 00:00:47.214 position:24% line:83% align:start
that the ships are
victims of secret

00:00:47.314 --> 00:00:48.516 position:7% line:89% align:start
weapons used by their enemies.

00:00:48.616 --> 00:00:53.186 position:5% line:83% align:start
The industrial world, meanwhile,
strengthens itself with steel.

00:00:53.287 --> 00:00:55.222 position:5% line:89% align:start
World powers growl at each other

00:00:55.322 --> 00:00:57.357 position:27% line:83% align:start
for new colonies
in Africa and Asia.

00:00:57.457 --> 00:00:59.393 position:24% line:83% align:start
The threats become
terrible warfare.

00:00:59.493 --> 00:01:01.796 position:24% line:83% align:start
As the 20th Century
draws closer,

00:01:01.896 --> 00:01:03.665 position:13% line:89% align:start
civilization grows richer,

00:01:03.765 --> 00:01:05.600 position:7% line:89% align:start
but the people tremble in fear,

00:01:05.700 --> 00:01:09.269 position:10% line:83% align:start
and the clouds of a world war
darken the horizon.

00:01:09.369 --> 00:01:13.140 position:16% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music playing]

00:01:16.878 --> 00:01:18.478 position:21% line:89% align:start
[singing in Japanese]

00:02:25.980 --> 00:02:27.280 position:21% line:89% align:start
[singing in Japanese]

00:02:38.926 --> 00:02:43.163 position:21% line:89% align:start
[soft music playing]

00:03:02.884 --> 00:03:04.519 position:30% line:89% align:start
Paris. Paris...

00:03:05.653 --> 00:03:07.522 position:24% line:89% align:start
[fireworks popping]

00:03:07.622 --> 00:03:08.422 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:03:09.957 --> 00:03:11.291 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ow.

00:03:11.391 --> 00:03:13.895 position:21% line:89% align:start
[seagulls screeching]

00:03:13.995 --> 00:03:16.196 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:03:16.296 --> 00:03:18.866 position:24% line:89% align:start
[fireworks popping]

00:03:21.969 --> 00:03:24.505 position:16% line:89% align:start
[gasps] The Eiffel Tower!

00:03:24.605 --> 00:03:25.372 position:16% line:5% align:start
[dramatic music playing]

00:03:29.544 --> 00:03:32.379 position:24% line:89% align:start
[fireworks popping]

00:03:34.347 --> 00:03:36.383 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Jean] What an incredible sight!

00:03:36.483 --> 00:03:38.820 position:5% line:89% align:start
So this is the Paris Exposition!

00:03:38.920 --> 00:03:41.689 position:24% line:89% align:start
[crowd chattering]

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:47.394 position:21% line:83% align:start
[guard] There will be
a wait of one hour.

00:03:47.494 --> 00:03:48.963 position:21% line:89% align:start
Please be courteous.

00:03:49.063 --> 00:03:50.732 position:35% line:89% align:start
No pushing.

00:03:50.832 --> 00:03:53.333 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[Tesla coil zapping]
-[crowd chattering]

00:03:54.635 --> 00:03:55.803 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Jean] Wow!

00:03:55.903 --> 00:03:58.271 position:27% line:89% align:start
Those look great!

00:03:58.371 --> 00:04:00.808 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's too bad they'll never
get off the ground.

00:04:03.511 --> 00:04:05.513 position:30% line:89% align:start
It sure is big!

00:04:05.613 --> 00:04:07.481 position:10% line:83% align:start
But they waste too much power
in the drive shaft.

00:04:10.317 --> 00:04:11.451 position:16% line:89% align:start
Looks like the crowds are

00:04:11.552 --> 00:04:12.720 position:30% line:83% align:start
more impressive
than the inventions.

00:04:14.822 --> 00:04:17.324 position:10% line:89% align:start
The competition is starting!

00:04:17.424 --> 00:04:19.326 position:5% line:89% align:start
[announcer] Welcome to the first

00:04:19.426 --> 00:04:21.028 position:21% line:83% align:start
International Flight
Competition.

00:04:21.129 --> 00:04:23.463 position:13% line:89% align:start
Today's contest will decide

00:04:23.564 --> 00:04:26.534 position:21% line:83% align:start
which airship can fly
the furthest distance.

00:04:26.634 --> 00:04:30.772 position:19% line:83% align:start
The grand prize winner
will receive 20,000 francs!

00:04:32.774 --> 00:04:34.709 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uncle!

00:04:34.809 --> 00:04:35.877 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:04:35.977 --> 00:04:37.712 position:13% line:89% align:start
I've been looking for you!

00:04:37.812 --> 00:04:40.047 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Sorry I'm late.
-You didn't miss much.

00:04:40.148 --> 00:04:42.750 position:30% line:83% align:start
The first one's
just getting ready to take off.

00:04:42.850 --> 00:04:45.452 position:24% line:83% align:start
You think it has a
chance, my boy?

00:04:45.553 --> 00:04:48.689 position:7% line:83% align:start
Those wings are far too flimsy
to support that engine.

00:04:51.458 --> 00:04:53.293 position:21% line:83% align:start
Given the wind speed,
there's no way

00:04:53.393 --> 00:04:54.962 position:21% line:83% align:start
it can fly more than,
oh, eight meters.

00:04:55.062 --> 00:04:57.598 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:04:57.698 --> 00:04:59.299 position:30% line:89% align:start
Look out below!

00:04:59.399 --> 00:05:02.435 position:21% line:89% align:start
[indistinct chatter]

00:05:04.404 --> 00:05:07.942 position:33% line:89% align:start
[crowd gasps]

00:05:08.042 --> 00:05:10.044 position:7% line:83% align:start
[announcer] The flight distance
for contestant number one

00:05:10.144 --> 00:05:11.712 position:27% line:89% align:start
was eight meters!

00:05:11.813 --> 00:05:13.080 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Like we said!
-Like we said!

00:05:13.181 --> 00:05:16.383 position:35% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
And now contestant number two!

00:05:16.483 --> 00:05:19.587 position:19% line:83% align:start
This airship has flown
over the White Cliffs of Dover.

00:05:19.687 --> 00:05:21.656 position:10% line:89% align:start
And it is by Lord Arkwright.

00:05:21.756 --> 00:05:24.391 position:27% line:89% align:start
And away he goes!

00:05:24.491 --> 00:05:27.460 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Lord Arkwright laughing]

00:05:27.562 --> 00:05:29.496 position:38% line:89% align:start
[screams]

00:05:30.932 --> 00:05:32.432 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:05:32.533 --> 00:05:34.101 position:10% line:89% align:start
Better luck next time, Lord!

00:05:34.202 --> 00:05:36.604 position:19% line:83% align:start
When is it going to be
our turn, Uncle?

00:05:36.704 --> 00:05:38.673 position:19% line:89% align:start
Oh, I apologize, Jean.

00:05:38.773 --> 00:05:40.508 position:24% line:89% align:start
I drew number 102.

00:05:40.608 --> 00:05:43.376 position:21% line:83% align:start
-The long wait, then?
-I'm afraid so.

00:05:43.476 --> 00:05:45.012 position:30% line:83% align:start
We could still
go take the aircraft

00:05:45.112 --> 00:05:46.514 position:10% line:89% align:start
off of the boat if you like.

00:05:46.614 --> 00:05:47.748 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Jean] Sure.

00:05:47.849 --> 00:05:49.016 position:33% line:89% align:start
[crowd moans]

00:06:01.596 --> 00:06:04.599 position:13% line:83% align:start
[uncle] Did you get seasick
during your travel?

00:06:04.699 --> 00:06:06.834 position:13% line:89% align:start
Yes, but nothing terrible.

00:06:06.934 --> 00:06:09.871 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well, I'm glad you
made it safely, my boy.

00:06:09.971 --> 00:06:11.772 position:21% line:83% align:start
You did a remarkable
amount of work

00:06:11.873 --> 00:06:12.940 position:13% line:89% align:start
while you were on the boat.

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:14.508 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Jean] Thank you.

00:06:14.609 --> 00:06:16.010 position:19% line:83% align:start
[uncle] I wish I could
have helped,

00:06:16.110 --> 00:06:17.912 position:27% line:83% align:start
but you know how
I am with watercraft.

00:06:18.012 --> 00:06:20.882 position:21% line:83% align:start
[laughs] Don't worry
about that, Uncle.

00:06:20.982 --> 00:06:24.417 position:24% line:83% align:start
Speaking of boats,
the Americans have commissioned

00:06:24.518 --> 00:06:26.988 position:27% line:83% align:start
a new battleship
to hunt down the sea monsters.

00:06:27.088 --> 00:06:30.524 position:13% line:83% align:start
Perhaps they'll get the one
that took your father.

00:06:30.625 --> 00:06:32.793 position:24% line:83% align:start
You know his death
hasn't been confirmed yet.

00:06:32.894 --> 00:06:36.163 position:10% line:89% align:start
Hmm. That's right. I forgot.

00:06:36.264 --> 00:06:38.032 position:19% line:83% align:start
-[announcer] Number 22.
-Huh?

00:06:38.132 --> 00:06:39.432 position:19% line:89% align:start
[announcer] The Pierre!

00:06:39.533 --> 00:06:41.102 position:16% line:89% align:start
That's the top contender!

00:06:41.202 --> 00:06:42.703 position:33% line:89% align:start
[crowd moans]

00:06:42.803 --> 00:06:46.173 position:21% line:83% align:start
[laughs] That was the
top contender.

00:06:46.274 --> 00:06:47.909 position:16% line:89% align:start
The grand prize is ours!

00:06:48.009 --> 00:06:50.912 position:30% line:83% align:start
It is, and by a
wide margin, too!

00:06:51.012 --> 00:06:52.513 position:35% line:89% align:start
It is ours!

00:06:52.613 --> 00:06:54.181 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:06:54.282 --> 00:06:56.651 position:21% line:83% align:start
Once we get our hands
on that kind of money,

00:06:56.751 --> 00:06:58.552 position:19% line:89% align:start
we will be able to make

00:06:58.653 --> 00:07:01.022 position:33% line:83% align:start
all kinds of
wonderful contraptions,

00:07:01.122 --> 00:07:04.457 position:21% line:83% align:start
and my mean, old wife
will finally stop complaining.

00:07:04.558 --> 00:07:05.693 position:13% line:89% align:start
But who cares if she does,

00:07:05.793 --> 00:07:07.028 position:13% line:89% align:start
because before we go home,

00:07:07.128 --> 00:07:08.930 position:24% line:83% align:start
we're going to have
some fun in Paris!

00:07:09.030 --> 00:07:10.932 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laughs]
-[uncle] Ooh, la, la!

00:07:11.032 --> 00:07:12.199 position:19% line:89% align:start
[bicycle bell jingles]

00:07:12.300 --> 00:07:14.434 position:19% line:83% align:start
[uncle] We can finance
an expedition

00:07:14.535 --> 00:07:16.203 position:16% line:89% align:start
to look for your father.

00:07:16.304 --> 00:07:19.073 position:5% line:83% align:start
Then you'll discover many pretty
girls that would like to meet

00:07:19.173 --> 00:07:20.574 position:33% line:83% align:start
a rich, young
genius like yourself.

00:07:20.675 --> 00:07:22.209 position:19% line:89% align:start
[bicycle bell jingles]

00:07:22.310 --> 00:07:24.578 position:16% line:83% align:start
[uncle] Always remember,
you only live once, Jean,

00:07:24.679 --> 00:07:27.480 position:24% line:83% align:start
so we have to make
the most of this opportunity.

00:07:28.716 --> 00:07:30.584 position:16% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music playing]

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:34.956 position:19% line:89% align:start
[bicycle bell jingles]

00:07:37.925 --> 00:07:40.795 position:13% line:83% align:start
Oh, Jean, could you hand me
the wrench, please? Hmm?

00:07:42.530 --> 00:07:44.231 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Ah.
-What is the matter, boy?

00:07:44.332 --> 00:07:46.167 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'll be back. Bye!

00:07:46.267 --> 00:07:47.835 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hey, what about the plane?

00:07:47.935 --> 00:07:49.971 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:07:50.071 --> 00:07:52.206 position:24% line:83% align:start
She's ready to go.
I'll be back to fly her later.

00:07:53.107 --> 00:07:54.909 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:07:55.009 --> 00:07:56.677 position:30% line:89% align:start
20,000 francs.

00:07:57.311 --> 00:08:00.181 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Grandis] I found her at last.

00:08:00.281 --> 00:08:04.452 position:13% line:83% align:start
It will be mine by tonight,
so make sure you don't lose her.

00:08:04.585 --> 00:08:05.886 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Right!
-Right!

00:08:05.987 --> 00:08:09.123 position:21% line:83% align:start
If my guess is right,
she'll go to the tower.

00:08:09.223 --> 00:08:13.127 position:16% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music playing]

00:08:31.645 --> 00:08:35.249 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Nadia] France, Spain, Italy,

00:08:35.349 --> 00:08:37.985 position:30% line:89% align:start
Egypt, Africa.

00:08:39.887 --> 00:08:43.090 position:10% line:83% align:start
King, do you think I was born
in Africa like you were?

00:08:43.190 --> 00:08:46.293 position:24% line:83% align:start
Or is it some place
we haven't even thought of yet?

00:08:46.394 --> 00:08:47.695 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[purrs]
-[chuckles]

00:08:47.795 --> 00:08:49.130 position:24% line:89% align:start
But I don't suppose

00:08:49.230 --> 00:08:51.098 position:30% line:83% align:start
you would know,
would you?

00:08:51.198 --> 00:08:53.634 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[purrs]
-[gasps]

00:08:53.734 --> 00:08:55.302 position:30% line:89% align:start
How wonderful.

00:08:55.403 --> 00:08:58.139 position:24% line:83% align:start
Maybe we would find
it if we could fly.

00:08:58.239 --> 00:09:00.107 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Jean] Oh, but you can fly.

00:09:00.207 --> 00:09:02.109 position:30% line:89% align:start
[nervous laugh]

00:09:02.209 --> 00:09:03.778 position:21% line:89% align:start
[purrs aggressively]

00:09:03.878 --> 00:09:07.214 position:27% line:83% align:start
My name is Jean,
Jean Roque Raltique, miss.

00:09:07.314 --> 00:09:10.184 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm an inventor.
I can help you fly.

00:09:10.284 --> 00:09:12.720 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[purrs aggressively]
-[scoffs]

00:09:12.820 --> 00:09:14.288 position:24% line:89% align:start
Uh, what is wrong?

00:09:14.388 --> 00:09:16.057 position:16% line:89% align:start
But don't you believe me?

00:09:17.725 --> 00:09:20.561 position:19% line:83% align:start
But it's true. You see,
I have a plane.

00:09:20.661 --> 00:09:22.063 position:5% line:89% align:start
I came all the way from Le Havre

00:09:22.163 --> 00:09:23.831 position:27% line:83% align:start
to compete in the
flying contest.

00:09:23.931 --> 00:09:26.333 position:27% line:83% align:start
Looks like you've
come a long way, too.

00:09:26.434 --> 00:09:28.903 position:5% line:89% align:start
Where are you from? Is it India?

00:09:30.104 --> 00:09:33.074 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry, but I won't give
such personal information

00:09:33.174 --> 00:09:35.042 position:19% line:89% align:start
to a complete stranger.

00:09:35.142 --> 00:09:38.112 position:16% line:83% align:start
Oh, good. You understood
what I was saying.

00:09:38.212 --> 00:09:40.014 position:7% line:83% align:start
I didn't know if we even spoke
the same language.

00:09:40.114 --> 00:09:41.582 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmph.

00:09:41.682 --> 00:09:43.250 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry,
but I didn't mean to offend you.

00:09:43.350 --> 00:09:45.086 position:41% line:89% align:start
Really?

00:09:45.186 --> 00:09:47.721 position:10% line:83% align:start
So, I don't suppose you find
my dark skin funny?

00:09:47.822 --> 00:09:49.223 position:41% line:89% align:start
Oh, no!

00:09:50.424 --> 00:09:52.193 position:35% line:89% align:start
Is that so?

00:09:52.293 --> 00:09:54.261 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well, then, what do
you want with me?

00:09:54.361 --> 00:09:57.031 position:21% line:83% align:start
Uh, I thought that we
could both become friends

00:09:57.131 --> 00:09:59.133 position:24% line:83% align:start
since we happen to
be in Paris together.

00:09:59.233 --> 00:10:00.267 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't you think?

00:10:00.367 --> 00:10:01.735 position:30% line:89% align:start
No, thank you.

00:10:05.106 --> 00:10:07.708 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-[purrs aggressively]

00:10:07.808 --> 00:10:09.243 position:24% line:89% align:start
What a strange cat.

00:10:09.343 --> 00:10:11.112 position:33% line:89% align:start
He's a lion.

00:10:11.212 --> 00:10:12.913 position:21% line:89% align:start
[purrs aggressively]

00:10:16.217 --> 00:10:18.385 position:13% line:89% align:start
Come now, don't be so dour.

00:10:18.486 --> 00:10:20.121 position:24% line:89% align:start
You only live once,

00:10:20.221 --> 00:10:23.257 position:13% line:83% align:start
so we have to make the most
of this opportunity!

00:10:24.925 --> 00:10:26.193 position:27% line:89% align:start
[crystal beeping]

00:10:26.293 --> 00:10:27.628 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:10:30.297 --> 00:10:32.900 position:5% line:89% align:start
What is that? Did you invent it?

00:10:35.870 --> 00:10:38.272 position:16% line:89% align:start
Well, King, we should go.

00:10:40.074 --> 00:10:43.244 position:10% line:83% align:start
You're too refined to create
such a scene in public.

00:10:43.344 --> 00:10:47.214 position:19% line:83% align:start
And I had to watch it,
and I'm so tired of watching it!

00:10:47.314 --> 00:10:50.251 position:21% line:83% align:start
Now, now, Ms. Granva,
don't be so hard on the kid.

00:10:50.351 --> 00:10:53.254 position:19% line:83% align:start
Yeah. Why don't we just
get down to business, Miss?

00:10:53.354 --> 00:10:55.089 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh, shut up!

00:10:55.189 --> 00:10:57.291 position:21% line:83% align:start
Now kindly hand over
your precious

00:10:57.391 --> 00:10:58.826 position:19% line:89% align:start
little bauble, my dear.

00:11:00.761 --> 00:11:03.998 position:7% line:83% align:start
Did you know that we have been
searching all over Europe

00:11:04.098 --> 00:11:06.133 position:27% line:83% align:start
for you and that
wonderful jewel?

00:11:07.468 --> 00:11:09.003 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh, give it here.

00:11:09.103 --> 00:11:11.172 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Nice and easy.
-Nice and easy.

00:11:11.272 --> 00:11:14.341 position:13% line:83% align:start
Now, boys, put those away.
She's just a girl.

00:11:14.441 --> 00:11:15.943 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right.

00:11:16.043 --> 00:11:17.778 position:16% line:89% align:start
Well, don't make me wait.

