00:16:37.565 --> 00:16:39.066 position:41% line:89% align:start
Nadia!

00:16:39.166 --> 00:16:40.334 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:16:40.434 --> 00:16:41.201 position:44% line:89% align:start
