00:17:12.867 --> 00:17:16.638 position:16% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music playing]

00:17:19.674 --> 00:17:22.242 position:21% line:83% align:start
You're just not used
to kind treatment.

00:17:22.342 --> 00:17:23.110 position:44% line:89% align:start
Here.

00:17:24.478 --> 00:17:26.079 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:17:26.179 --> 00:17:28.783 position:7% line:83% align:start
