00:19:05.412 --> 00:19:06.313 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'll stop him.

00:19:06.948 --> 00:19:08.415 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Grandis] Let him be.

00:19:08.516 --> 00:19:10.752 position:13% line:89% align:start
