00:21:19.914 --> 00:21:21.682 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gunshot]

00:21:21.783 --> 00:21:22.850 position:35% line:89% align:start
[screaming]

00:21:26.854 --> 00:21:29.056 position:24% line:83% align:start
